<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>

<activity xml:id="act-compararDosAlgoritmosDeResta" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ol>
      <li>In the first algorithm, the first step is decomposing one of the hundreds into 10 tens. In the second algorithm, the first step is subtracting the ones. Each algorithm will look the same at the end.</li>
      <li>283</li>
    </ol>
  </solution>


